Run the following codes in order to start the server

chmod u+x run.bat #gives permission to run the server-starter
chmod +x ngrok #gives permission to run the ip forwarder

ngrok authtoken 2dhAVtxTLrsce4uFj7i423YCw4n_789LKYtxpHy1MSqPDBJEr #sets up the authkey for port forwarding

ngrok tcp 25565 #starts a node at port 25565

#make a new terminal

./run.bat
